Package: ubuntu-hibernate-wizard
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Ubuntu Hibernate Wizard Project <example@example.org>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, pkexec, polkitd, initramfs-tools, grub-common, util-linux, e2fsprogs
Recommends: mokutil, gnome-shell
Description: GUI wizard to enable, repair, and verify hibernation on Ubuntu
 Guides the user through creating swap, setting resume=UUID and
 resume_offset kernel parameters, updating GRUB and initramfs, and
 verifying the configuration after reboot. Crash-safe swap resize,
 backups, and one-click repair of stale resume offsets.
